				\begin{document}$$\sigma _i = \frac{L}{{Z\prime A}}$$\end{document}, where Z′ is taken at the frequency when the phase angle is closest to 0 (as shown in Supplementary Figure 1), L is the distance between the two electrodes, and A is the area of the electrodes.
